    <description># [color=clay]The Crier (Neutral Social)[/color]

_Immune to Convert_

*Passive: Public Service - Thanks to being a Public service, you will be protected by officials at night, unable to be killed but you can&#39;t whisper to anyone.*

*Passive: Public Speaker - Whenever you say the full name of a player, they will be alerted by a bell sound*

**Day Ability 1: Announcement (3 uses)**
The next thing you type will be slightly larger text than the rest of the chat.

**Day Ability 2: Headline (2 use)**
The next thing you type will appear in front of everyone&#39;s screen for 10 seconds.

**Night Ability 1: Newsletter (2 uses)**
Choose a living target, reveal their Journal to everyone in the beginning of the day, but not who&#39;s it is.

_Goal: Get at least 5 people to say a given phrase without asking anyone to say it. Once somebody says the phrase, you&#39;ll recieve a little bell sound. Once 5 people have said the phrase, a large bell will sound._

Phrases could include:

&gt; Unicorns Don&#39;t Exist
&gt; Praise Adiart
&gt; Praise Mithras
&gt; Praise Corax
&gt; Praise Teemo
&gt; Trial By Combat

@TeaHacker approved, I wasn&#39;t going to post this until he convinced me :thumbsup:</description>
    
